'''Umar Krupp''', ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Gana]] na producer.  Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime ''House of Gold'' na ''Amakye na Dede'' .

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye i [[Accra]], muri [[Gana]].

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2015, yatsindiye igihembo cy'umukinnyi witwaye neza muri Pan Africa Cinema Awards (PACA). 

Krupp yatowe nka Producer mwiza wa [[Afurika]] muri Nollywood Entertainment and Leadership Awards (NELAS) muri 2019 kubera gukora firime ''Accra Hustlers'' .  Muri 2019, Krupp yayoboye ''Ama'' yasohotse mu ikinamico muri Mutarama 2020.  Muri 2018, yakinnye muri filime ''Babani'' . Nyuma yaje gutsindira ibihembo bine muri Golden Movie Awards harimo; City People Entertainment Award for Face of Ghana Movies.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://12framesonline.com/2018/06/youngest-producer-actor-umar-krupp-tops-ghanaians-with-four-4-awards-at-the-golden-movie-awards/|title=Youngest Producer /Actor Umar Krupp tops Ghanaians with four -4 Awards at the Golden Movie Awards|publisher=12framesonline|accessdate=19 October 2020}}</ref>Muri 2020, umukinnyi wa filime Serwaa Akoto uri hafi kuza yaburiye umukinnyi Umar Krupp ku bijyanye no gutandukana na Krupp no kwishyura ibibazo umukinnyi wa filime.   

